Fixes and Improvements in 2.16.6
- Photos: fixed a memory leak while exporting photos
- Photos: fixed a rare crash "PhotoIconConverter.Convert - System.ComponentModel.Win32Exception" while browsing the device photo library, it was actually not fixed in 2.16.5 (Windows)
- Date range filters: the date picker is now behaving properly (macOS)
- Music: tracks meta data is now exported properly to Music or iTunes (macOS)
- Backup browsing: browsing backup archives now works as expected
- Files: this section is now properly displayed when browsing new backups, on old backups the section might still not appear properly
- Messages & WhatsApp: fixed a rare issue while exporting attachments: "Cannot write local file..."
